#. Translators: message asking the user if he wants to decline creating the data folder in the home user directory.
#: addon\installTasks.py:31
msgid ""
"Creating folder to store data files in home user directory ...\n"
"You can press on Cancel button to skipt this, and adjust this later from the "
"addon's settings dialog,Do you wants to proceed in creating the addons data "
"folder in your home user directory?"
